 (Spanish) To the Solano family, I want to tell them to  forgive me. While I am still alive I bring suffer to you all.  The harm  that I did to your dad and husband, I hope this brings you closure to all of  you.  I never wanted to hurt any of you all.  I received your card  and I want to thank you all. (English) For my family I love you all very much.  No  matter what, remember my promise, no matter what, I will always be with you,  please keep my promise. (Spanish) To Maricela I want to pass my spirit to my  mother-in-law, I leave you all with peace. (English) I love you all, Warden I’m ready.
